bio: Research and Investment Partner at Woodstock Fund
contributionDescription: Ecosystem Project Idea: Awesome Optimism Repository #94. The 'Awesome Optimism' repository, akin to the widely popular 'awesome X' repositories found throughout GitHub aims to showcase the vibrant open-source contributions happening within the Optimism ecosystem, including notable projects like Magi, op-erigon, and others.
impactDescription:
• Provides a centralized resource for developers and enthusiasts to discover projects in the Optimism ecosystem.
• Encourages open-source contributions and fosters a stronger community around Optimism.
• Offers visibility and recognition for projects contributing to the Optimism ecosystem.
